		(2)[label=)] <m>\displaystyle \lim_{x \to +\infty} { \left( \dfrac{3x-5}{3x-2} \right)^{2x^2}}</m>
	</p>

	<p>
		<m>\displaystyle \lim_{x \to +\infty} { \left( \dfrac{5x-2}{5x+3} \right)^{3x}}</m>
